00:06:25.170 --> 00:06:28.500
when you're seeing a gamma rays
burst is the birth of a black hole

00:06:28.500 --> 00:06:30.420
in a very distant galaxy.

00:06:30.420 --> 00:06:35.150
And I think one of the other things
